
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-komiya-mmusic-session-mobility-usecases-00.txt'>
    <title>"Use Cases for Session Mobility in Multimedia Applications", Diasaku Komiya'</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-komiya-mmusic-session-mobility-usecases-00.txt</link>
    <description>Session mobility allows a user to transfer an ongoing session from one device to another device. This document attempts to summarize the use cases for session mobility in multimedia applications. For each use case, we provide possible motivation for the user to initiate a session transfer from one device to another.</description>
    <dc:date>2006-03-01T08:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
